# Psychotic Disorders

Educational materials on psychotic disorders, focusing on clinically relevant concepts for learners and healthcare professionals.

## Purpose
- Summarize core features of psychotic disorders
- Support clinical reasoning and differential diagnosis
- Provide structured, accessible content in Portuguese

## Planned subtopics
- Core symptoms and psychopathology
- Diagnostic categories and clinical profiles
- Differential diagnosis
- Functional impact and risk assessment
- Overview of treatment strategies
- Patient and family education

> Note: Content in this repository is for educational purposes only and does not replace formal clinical training or individualized medical care.
